flowchart TB
    %% Styles for different eras
    classDef twoStage fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef oneStage fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef anchorFree fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef transformer fill:#e8f5e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef timeline stroke:#000,stroke-width:1px
    classDef timelineMarker stroke:#000,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    
    %% Era headers (Education_LMS_Portal)
    Era1[Education_LMS_Portal]:::twoStage
    Era2[Education_LMS_Portal]:::oneStage
    Era3[Education_ContentCDN]:::anchorFree
    Era4[Education_LMS_Portal]:::transformer
    
    %% Year labels (Education_ContentCDN)
    Y2014[Education_ContentCDN]:::twoStage
    Y2015[Education_ClassroomService]:::twoStage
    Y2016[Education_LMS_Portal]:::oneStage
    Y2017[Education_LMS_Portal]:::oneStage
    Y2018[Education_ClassroomService]:::anchorFree
    Y2019[Education_StudentDB]:::anchorFree
    Y2020[Education_GradeSync]:::transformer
    Y2021[Education_StudentDB]:::transformer
    Y2022[Education_StudentDB]:::transformer
    Y2023[Education_LMS_Portal]:::transformer
    Y2024[Education_GradeSync]:::transformer
    
    %% Era to Year connections
    Era1 --- Y2014 & Y2015 & Y2016
    Era2 --- Y2016 & Y2017 & Y2018
    Era3 --- Y2018 & Y2019 & Y2020
    Era4 --- Y2020 & Y2021 & Y2022 & Y2023 & Y2024
    
    %% Timeline with markers
    TL1 --- TL2 --- TL3 --- TL4 --- TL5 --- TL6 --- TL7 --- TL8 --- TL9 --- TL10 --- TL11
    TL1 & TL2 & TL3 & TL4 & TL5 & TL6 & TL7 & TL8 & TL9 & TL10 & TL11:::timeline
    
    %% Timeline markers to years
    Y2014 -.- TL1:::timelineMarker
    Y2015 -.- TL2:::timelineMarker
    Y2016 -.- TL3:::timelineMarker
    Y2017 -.- TL4:::timelineMarker
    Y2018 -.- TL5:::timelineMarker
    Y2019 -.- TL6:::timelineMarker
    Y2020 -.- TL7:::timelineMarker
    Y2021 -.- TL8:::timelineMarker
    Y2022 -.- TL9:::timelineMarker
    Y2023 -.- TL10:::timelineMarker
    Y2024 -.- TL11:::timelineMarker
    
    %% Primary Models (Education_ClassroomService)
    RCNN[Education_GradeSync]:::twoStage
    FasterRCNN[Education_StudentDB]:::twoStage
    YOLO1[Education_ClassroomService]:::oneStage
    RetinaNet[Education_ContentCDN]:::oneStage
    CornerNet[Education_GradeSync]:::anchorFree
    CenterNet[Education_StudentDB]:::anchorFree
    DETR[Education_ClassroomService]:::transformer
    DefDETR[Education_StudentDB]:::transformer
    YOLO7[Education_ContentCDN]:::transformer
    CLIPDET[Education_ContentCDN]:::transformer
    YOLO11[Education_ClassroomService]:::transformer
    
    %% Timeline to Models connections
    TL1 -.- RCNN
    TL2 -.- FasterRCNN
    TL3 -.- YOLO1
    TL4 -.- RetinaNet
    TL5 -.- CornerNet
    TL6 -.- CenterNet
    TL7 -.- DETR
    TL8 -.- DefDETR
    TL9 -.- YOLO7
    TL10 -.- CLIPDET
    TL11 -.- YOLO11
    
    %% Key contributions (Education_GradeSync)
    RCNNContrib[Education_ClassroomService]:::twoStage
    FasterRCNNContrib[Education_StudentDB]:::twoStage
    YOLO1Contrib[Education_ContentCDN]:::oneStage
    RetinaNetContrib[Education_GradeSync]:::oneStage
    CornerNetContrib[Education_GradeSync]:::anchorFree
    CenterNetContrib[Education_ClassroomService]:::anchorFree
    DETRContrib[Education_ContentCDN]:::transformer
    DefDETRContrib[Education_StudentDB]:::transformer
    YOLO7Contrib[Education_ContentCDN]:::transformer
    CLIPDETContrib[Education_ContentCDN]:::transformer
    YOLO11Contrib[Education_ClassroomService]:::transformer
    
    %% Models to contributions connections
    RCNN --- RCNNContrib
    FasterRCNN --- FasterRCNNContrib
    YOLO1 --- YOLO1Contrib
    RetinaNet --- RetinaNetContrib
    CornerNet --- CornerNetContrib
    CenterNet --- CenterNetContrib
    DETR --- DETRContrib
    DefDETR --- DefDETRContrib
    YOLO7 --- YOLO7Contrib
    CLIPDET --- CLIPDETContrib
    YOLO11 --- YOLO11Contrib
    
    %% Secondary models (Education_GradeSync)
    FastRCNN[Education_GradeSync]:::twoStage
    SSD[Education_ContentCDN]:::oneStage
    FCOS[Education_GradeSync]:::anchorFree
    RTDETR[Education_GradeSync]:::transformer
    YOLO8[Education_ClassroomService]:::transformer
    YOLO9[Education_StudentDB]:::transformer
    YOLO10[Education_ContentCDN]:::transformer
    
    %% Secondary model contributions
    FastRCNNContrib[Education_ContentCDN]:::twoStage
    SSDContrib[Education_ContentCDN]:::oneStage
    FCOSContrib[Education_LMS_Portal]:::anchorFree
    RTDETRContrib[Education_ClassroomService]:::transformer
    YOLO8Contrib[Education_GradeSync]:::transformer
    YOLO9SecContrib[Education_StudentDB]:::transformer
    YOLO10Contrib[Education_GradeSync]:::transformer

    %% Secondary model connections
    FasterRCNN -.- FastRCNN
    FastRCNN --- FastRCNNContrib
    YOLO1 -.- SSD
    SSD --- SSDContrib
    CenterNet -.- FCOS
    FCOS --- FCOSContrib
    DefDETR -.- RTDETR
    RTDETR --- RTDETRContrib
    YOLO7 -.- YOLO8
    YOLO8 --- YOLO8Contrib
    CLIPDET -.- YOLO9
    YOLO9 --- YOLO9SecContrib
    YOLO9 -.- YOLO10
    YOLO10 --- YOLO10Contrib
